metadata.description:
Limited Edition of 33 NFT's made by Eboshi for VLVT

Why Frog?

Frogs represent WISDOM (knowledge) because they can adapt and make quick decisions. They also symbolize WEALTH due to their association with water, which is seen as a source of prosperity. Additionally, frogs represent LONG TERM GOALS because of their ability to transform and the importance of persistence and patience in achieving desired outcomes.
